Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is a bad thing that the university require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. First of all, living on campus is always expensive than living off campus. Secondly, we might not have the ability to choose the roommate so we could live with someone we do not like.